      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "was for the carriage, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "namely, of the voice. He was the moderator of the music, instructing them when and how to lift up their voice, change their notes, or make stops. Accordingly, the following words tell us, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "he instructed about song — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Or taught them how to sing; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "because he was skilful — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Was a great artist in singing.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
